y allege the project lacks environmental clearance and other approvals, with activists citing regulatory violations and environmental damage. Officials assured the matter would be reviewed.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/karapur-villagers-demand-halt-to-luxury-housing-project-by-abhinandan-lodha/131697591?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-91096/131697591.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}